---
title: Loaded Spiced Wedges with Caramelised Onion & Mashed Avocado
description: Everyone loves potato wedges, that’s why we turned them into a hearty vegetarian meal. To make it work, we enlisted a few flavour-packed helping hands – beans, corn, caramelised onions and smashed avocado, plus a scattering of melted cheese. Now, it’s time to move wedges from the side to the main part of your plate!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5bc523ffae08b552b7251562-9ac6feb3.jpg
